{{Infobox company | name = Banco Interatlântico| type = [[Commercial bank]]ing| company_slogan = | foundation = July 1999| location = [[Praia]], [[Santiago, Cape Verde|Santiago]], [[Cape Verde]]| key_people = | num_employees = | industry = | products = | revenue = | homepage = {{url|http://www.bi.cv}}| }}
'''Banco Interatlântico''' is a [[Cape Verde]]an [[commercial bank]]. Its headquarter is at [[Avenida Cidade de Lisboa]] in [[Praia]].<ref>[https://www.cgd.pt/English/Contacts/International-Network/Pages/Banco-InterAtlantico-Cabo-Verde.aspx Banco InterAtlântico], CGD Group</ref> The bank was established in July 1999 as a subsidiary of the Portuguese [[Caixa Geral de Depósitos]]. The CGD Group now owns 70% of Banco Interatlântico.<ref>[http://www.bi.cv/Conteudos/Artigos/detalhe.aspx?idc=332&idsc=398&idl=2 History], Banco Interatlântico</ref>
