The '''Church of Assumption of Our Lady, Căuşeni''' ({{lang-ro|Biserica "Adormirea Maicii Domnului" din Căuşeni}}) is a historical monument in [[Căuşeni]], [[Moldova]].
The church was painted in 1763 by Stanciul Radu şi Voicul.
